{"tid":752913,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"學車台 駕院師父問題","createTime":"2018-07-23T07:50:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-31T04:44:16.000Z","uid":80140,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"665d434edd8e9da5ef584a5434718cb30eacb861","tid":752913,"uid":80140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T07:50:04.000Z","msg":"今日學緊第三堂<br />\n仲有五堂<br />\n<br />\n第一堂果個陣佢已經一開波問我加唔加堂 有個plan 五堂定七堂<br />\n三千左右<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係我心諗 第一堂咋wo 未知進度點 咁快sell鳩我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而且佢教果陣都好少講野 <br />\n時間又夾唔q度 又話星期日佢放假<br />\n我話我放工夜晚學八點半 佢又話唔得 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又想我閒日早上學<br />\n但係我份工唔得 多數放星期六日<br />\n就係夾唔到時間先簡駕院 貪佢時間彈性<br />\n而家咩都唔得 <br />\n第二堂去又問我加唔加堂 又話八堂唔夠 又話上堂個學生都加左 都唔知係咪有傭金收<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果八堂真係唔夠點解唔一開始買plan比夠13堂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c01cdc0ffbdeeb8c700e26c0bb26931098013290","tid":752913,"uid":87358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T08:13:13.000Z","msg":"出面師傅易就時間好多<br />\n通常駕丸都只為佢條考試路線<br />\n要學都出面補鐘"},{"pid":"a0ce0a87b7689bae05b48398154c985282089437","tid":752913,"uid":71596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T08:15:49.000Z","msg":"邊間？<br />\n我之前報觀駕 1take"},{"pid":"a4080864c76f343b253390afd30148d4a5ef0b22","tid":752913,"uid":80140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c01cdc0ffbdeeb8c700e26c0bb26931098013290","tid":752913,"uid":87358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T08:13:13.000Z","msg":"出面師傅易就時間好多<br />\n通常駕丸都只為佢條考試路線<br />\n要學都出面補鐘"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T08:19:29.000Z","msg":"仲諗住駕院多師父 book堂都容易d<br />\n我都諗緊 要補出去補算 <br />\n教得好就話 教唔好等於掉錢出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1791eb850237b79e4978f7dccf4fb5bf0403958d","tid":75291